@@CreateCalculatorForm
<TITLE CreateCalculatorForm function>
Summary
  Creates a calculator dialog.
Description
  Call CreateCalculatorForm to create a calculator dialog that will be used several times in an
  application.
Note
  CreateCalculatorForm does not display the dialog form. The application must display this form when
  it is needed by calling its ShowModal method.
Parameters
  AOwner       - The owner of the dialog.
  AHelpContext - Context number for online Help.
See Also
  CreatePopupCalculator, TJvCalculator

